divs: sighting detailshonolulu hawaii over looking kahala. was using my new camcorder i got for x-mas to zoom in on the city and then appeared some star like lights. it started off as two lights and they were moving in unison together. i was not sure what it was so i just followed it with my camera. the lights were so far away that i could not see them with the naked eye. i could only see them through the view finder. as it moved behind a building i went ahead and started to record. the two lights turned into three. then the three turned into four. all lights were traveling at a constant speed with one another so that made me feel like it was one piece instead of each light being separate. the distance of the craft was pretty far away. a rough guess would be that the craft was about 700-1500 ft long. i used this as a reference by noticing it went behind haunama bay which is very far away. i have pictures and videos that i uploaded to youtube because when i try uploading it on here, it kept giving me error messages. http:\\www.youtube.com\watch?v=fjb2xvqq3ss http:\\www.youtube.com\watch?v=lt8tydazqhq&feature=channel http:\\www.youtube.com\watch?v=cgmq1rkylym&feature=channel http:\\www.youtube.com\watch?v=2emtzq5dvis&feature=channel
